{"tid":2303211,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連續11年紀錄破功！AKB48紅白落選　遭批人氣慘下滑","createTime":"2020-11-27T17:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T19:11:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"828b88058d9c7fc7c516ce3559be736b6c046eda","tid":2303211,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"日本國民女團AKB48是相當具代表性的大型女團，自2005年出道之後，歷代成員在位時都大受歡迎，尤其是第一代「神七」的7位團員更是塑造經典。然而近日第71屆「NHK紅白歌唱大賽」表演名單公佈之後，結果AKB 48竟沒有入選，讓連續11年開唱的紀錄破功，引發了一陣不小熱議！<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906241-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906241-PH.jpg&h=7ec054cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本人氣女團AKB48落選2020年紅白演出。（圖／翻攝自AKB48 IG）<br />\n<br />\n每年「NHK紅白歌唱大賽」可說是每年在歲末時日本演藝圈的大事，尤其是歌手可以站上紅白的演出，幾乎可以說是一個當紅的里程碑代表，而AKB48自2009年開始，連續入選紅白歌唱大賽的演出陣容，除2008年中斷一次以外，AKB48一連入選11屆的演出，可說是在演藝圈舉足輕重。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906246-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906246-PH.jpg&h=57fb414c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲AKB48自2009年連續入選11年紀錄破功。（圖／翻攝自AKB48 IG）<br />\n<br />\n沒想到這個紀錄在2020年劃下休止符，NHK電視台表示，沒有邀請AKB48是「綜合考慮做出的選擇。」有網友分析，近年來AKB48除受限武漢肺炎疫情之外，並沒有甚麼熱門的人氣歌曲，於日本的影響力慢慢退減，相較過去鼎盛時期相比確實差了許多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/27/2906247-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F27%2F2906247-PH.jpg&h=96759e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲AKB48今年沒有甚麼熱門的人氣歌曲。（圖／翻攝自AKB48 IG）<br />\n<br />\n而AKB48總監督向井地美音也發文向粉絲致歉，她表示「沒能將前輩所傳承給自己的能量好好交接下去，比什麼都還令人感到抱歉及慚愧。」強調會好好繼續努力，而不少成員也發文曝光自己的心聲，連已畢業的成員們，也發文安慰鼓勵現役成員。"},{"pid":"c15fae2813411a01abefe7871c5a93ae6f1cd95a","tid":2303211,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"多人運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9addc69c6f96cc55db4e69d53cae3dac3a3bca6a","tid":2303211,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"同twice比 真係垃圾<br />\n今年紅白冇twice 紅白都係垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ac8bee9f428836ec07f2ee9053be9a5f3cee62","tid":2303211,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9addc69c6f96cc55db4e69d53cae3dac3a3bca6a","tid":2303211,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"同twice比 真係垃圾<br />\n今年紅白冇twice 紅白都係垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"咪咀跳舞都唔知上去做咩<br />\n個節目人氣不再"},{"pid":"ff327e97f5312f02e0ed68321595daafc77312e9","tid":2303211,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9addc69c6f96cc55db4e69d53cae3dac3a3bca6a","tid":2303211,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"同twice比 真係垃圾<br />\n今年紅白冇twice 紅白都係垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"求twice上去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369b91806b5b92001400872e2cd6a0a201c2181e","tid":2303211,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c15fae2813411a01abefe7871c5a93ae6f1cd95a","tid":2303211,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"多人運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"下海下海下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51db8d175586ae31ef6b20f6bda9426261186b2c","tid":2303211,"uid":39383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T00:17:30.000Z","msg":"係肥康無心經營, 玩坂系玩到上晒腦"},{"pid":"4e56d237de11935bb59632423a3f43b6e1b4e2